entries.femaleVariant: Gave us incomplete info again, the bitch.
Naw, naw, cheddar's fine. Just lookin' for an explanation. I mean, that's a big gig you had me botch, feel me?
What now? Call for backup? Crack some heads open, drag the bodies inside?
Your license has been revoked. Japantown – you gotta ghost outta there, got it?
Sham, hang on just a little longer, choom. Ripper's on the way.
I told you, dog. Afterlife's all about rep, the respect you command. Badge don't mean a thing, here.
Doors're shut to us – that's that. Tough cookies and move on.
Incredible. Just fucking incredible.
Cunt Rogue think she's above the law?
Whoa, man – quiet down! She hear that, she shoot your balls off. I don't wanna get hit by no ricochet.
Seriously thought you'd dick over the fixer? That was your best idea for some quick scratch?
We know how they're geared out – big fuckin' beans. We got no idea how many're holed up in that bunker.
We'll be good. Sham is our lucky charm. Eh, Sham?
Whoa, watch out – might just answer you. We best focus on the gig.
Now look, we send drones up first, make sure we don't land in a pool of hot, runny shit.
Fuuuck, rotten luck. Why aren't we at a hospital?
Might not come after us here. Aaargh... fuck. Say somethin', Sham, anythin'?
Whaddaya mean you not comin'? You comin', dawg. You'll be here in five minutes flat or-- Fuuck!
See… homiecide's not my customary MO. Wanna 'least know the reasons why, right? Tha'ss just me and my need.
I mean, who you holdin' in that bunker? Some unknown heir to the Arasaka empire? Haha.
Mhm... Next day, I was a pariah, she'd cut me off completely. Nobody would take my calls. Was like I was dead.
Good thing you only tested Regina. She's gentle. Any other fixer…? You'da had multiple fractures in both legs.
No fuckin' way. I wanna talk to Wakako.
So call 'er, dude. She's sure to wanna know your mind on this, heh.
